Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.56,0:22:48.08,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}ale zastaví sa pre tých, čo ostali sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:55.23,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}yume mamoru shirabe kuchizusamu no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:55.35,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Nôtim si melódiu, čo chráni naše sny,
