Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:59.78,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}aby každý mohol zaspať sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:02.45,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}mata au hi no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:02.45,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Spať, túžiac znova sa stretnúť
