Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.54,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}yasashisa wo sasoru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.54,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Dobro zvíťazí tak,
