Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:52.82,EpTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(722,487)}{\pos(443,377)}Popolavá noc
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:52.82,EpTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs32\pos(725,540)}Nabudúce
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokiaľ ide o onigiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.89,0:23:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ak ti naozaj chutí, musíš skúsiť toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je s kakaovou príchuťou a-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blázon!
